{"id":"api/core/viewChild","title":"viewChild","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/viewChild\", \"name\": \"viewChild\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/authoring/queries.ts#L78-L83\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"viewchild\">viewChild<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/viewChild#viewchild\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label dev-preview\" title=\"此 API 仅供开发者预览\">\n      <a href=\"guide/releases#developer-preview\">开发者预览</a>\n    </label>\n    \n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a4ov9d2bn3izhvs7legrisvxb\">初始化一个视图子查询。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/viewChild#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/core/viewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">viewChild</a>: <a href=\"api/core/ViewChildFunction\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChildFunction</a>;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/viewChild#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c53mkthihi0417qtx33vbs1g8\">考虑使用viewChild.required进行应该始终匹配的查询。</p>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c71yk7sa3d3tbyjbn7u6p796w\">进一步的信息可在\n<a href=\"api/core/viewChild#usage-notes\">使用说明...</a>中找到。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/viewChild#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ckilv6i8uz5yc908oh7r15nu9\">通过声明一个类字段并用viewChild()函数初始化它，在你的组件中创建一个子查询。</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({template: '&lt;div #el&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;my-component #cmp /&gt;'})\nexport class TestComponent {\n  divEl = <a href=\"api/core/viewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">viewChild</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a>&gt;('el');                   // <a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a>|undefined&gt;\n  divElRequired = viewChild.required&lt;<a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a>&gt;('el');  // <a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a>&gt;\n  cmp = <a href=\"api/core/viewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">viewChild</a>(MyComponent);                          // <a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a>&lt;MyComponent|undefined&gt;\n  cmpRequired = viewChild.required(MyComponent);         // <a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a>&lt;MyComponent&gt;\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/ViewChildFunction\n - errors/NG0951\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n - guide/signal-queries\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/ElementRef\n - api/core/Signal\n - api/core/ViewChildFunction\n - api/core/viewChild#description\n - api/core/viewChild#usage-notes\n - api/core/viewChild#viewchild\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/authoring/queries.ts#L78-L83\n-->"}